narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Make sure you and your readers understand the deadlines and what is expected from you.
Definitely do it. It is so rewarding to write a paper that is your own idea that is substantial. It might be the thing I am most proud of during my time at yale.
